# FimTyper CLI (Under Construction)

## Project Status

This repository contains a maintained command-line implementation of FimTyper, originally developed by the Center for Genomic Epidemiology at the Technical University of Denmark.

Original repository (03-10-2022):

<https://bitbucket.org/genomicepidemiology/fimtyper/>

The original software primarily supports a web interface. The CLI component is not actively maintained. This fork restores and modernizes the command-line tool for use in reproducible bioinformatics workflows and package managers.

Major updates in this fork include:

- Restored CLI functionality
- Packaging support for Spack and Bioconda
- Improved documentation

## Installation

### Installation via Spack

```shell
spack install fimtyper
```

### Installation via bioconda

```shell
conda create -n fimtyper fimtyper-cli -c bioconda -c conda-forge
```

