## Citation

If you use the fimH typing method implemented in this software, please cite the original publication:

[Roer L et al. 2017. Development of a web tool for Escherichia coli
subtyping based on fimH alleles. J Clin Microbiol.](https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28592545/)

If using this maintained CLI implementation, please also cite this repository:

Miller C. 2026.
fimtyper-cli. <https://github.com/dantaslab/fimtyper-cli>

## Relationship to the CGE Web Service

This repository is not affiliated with or maintained by the
Center for Genomic Epidemiology web services.

The official web implementation can be accessed at: <https://cge.cbs.dtu.dk/services/FimTyper/>

